extendedInfo.description: This app is for the 28th Annual Meeting of the Orthopaedic Trauma Association (OTA). The OTA Annual Meeting is for the benefit of orthopaedic trauma surgeons and related allied healthcare professionals through the presentation of peer-reviewed original basic science and clinical research papers, posters and symposia. Annual Meeting and related event participants can earn 19.5+ CME.Keywords: Trauma, Orthopaedic, Orthopaedic Trauma, OTA, Annual Meeting, 28th Annual Meeting, 2012
